ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.algorithm

Class DijkstraDistance

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.algorithm.AbstractAlgorithm
      • ch.bfh.ti.gravis.core.algorithm.DijkstraDistance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAlgorithm

     class DijkstraDistance
extends AbstractAlgorithm
    This implementation of dijkstra algorithm is based on pseudocode-description at:
    http://www-m9.ma. tum.de/Allgemeines/DijkstraCode
    A priority queue is used in order to determine the vertex with the minimum distance.
    The shortest predecessor is set for all solved vertices. All unreachable vertices are marked in the graph.
    Author:
    Patrick Kofmel (kofmp1@bfh.ch)
